bc-hrbl (1.1.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Rebuilt against libbc-hrbl 1.1.0, which adds quoted path segments
    to the query grammar. bc-hrbl query FILE "root.'some.key'.digest"
    now works on keys containing dots (e.g. file paths).
  * Build-Depends: libbc-hrbl-dev (>= 1.1.0).

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Thu, 23 Apr 2026 19:15:00 +0000

bc-hrbl (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Subcommands verify / query / inspect / convert.
  * Built on libbc-hrbl (>= 1.0.0) and bc-runtime CLI framework.
  * Full sanitizer and cppcheck coverage; e2e tests exercise the
    installed binary.

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Thu, 23 Apr 2026 14:00:00 +0000
